    <h1>Getting Started on Butts with Node.js</h1>
    <p>This is a sample Node application deployed to Butts. It's a reasonably simple app - but a good foundation for understanding how to get the most out of the Butts platform.</p>
    <a type="button" class="btn btn-lg btn-default" href="https://devcenter.Butts.com/articles/getting-started-with-nodejs"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-flash"></span> Getting Started on Butts with Node.js</a>
